His Grace the Lord Primate presided at the religious function; Dr. Devitt, Bishop of Raphoe, officiated as bishop celebrant at the Pontifical High Mass. Mr. R. S. Swaby, professor of music, St. Charles College, Notting-hill, London, was the organist, and Mr. Telford, junior, conducted. The organ is of large size and singularly beautiful appearancé, the case being forty feet high and thirty feet. wide.
